snippet: Russell Henley won his PGA Tour debut last weekend and is three shots off the lead at the Humana Challenge.
abstract: Russell Henley is three shots off lead at Humana Challenge golf tournament, and is poised to become the first in PGA Tour history to win his first two starts.
lead_paragraph: Russell Henley won his PGA Tour debut last weekend and is three shots off the lead at the Humana Challenge.

headline.seo: PGA Tour Rookie Russell Henley Off to Blazing Start
headline.main: Tour Rookie May Soon Be an Unknown No Longer
